summary: UA University is now accepting applications! (RP Group)
title: UA University is now accepting applications! (RP Group)
body:
We’re a low commitment Discord-based RP server based around a University AU. All characters mainly communicate through a group chat.

We have a ton of openings for sought after characters such as:

  • Midoriya Izuku
  • Ochaco Uraraka
  • Tenya Iida
  • Kirishima Eijirou
  • Denki Kaminari
  • Shinsou Hitoshi
  • Sero Hanta

And tons more!

UA University is Japan’s most prestigious general education institute. They offer degrees in almost every possible area of study. If you can dream it, you can study it at UA!  There are also many teaching opportunities at UA University and compensation is first-rate!

There are no quirks in this AU, but diverse physical appearances are normal! All physical characteristics associated with your character’s quirk will still be present, it’s just the quirk won’t be! This is to allow all characters to be on an equal playing field, and hopefully allow hero, villain, and student characters to be able to interact!

Please read all rules before applying!

MASTERLIST

blog.name: asktogatadad
blog.title: Ask_TogataDad
blog.description: Greetings! I am Togata Setsuna, single dad of lovely son named Mirio. I love telling my story so be the guest to ask questions!

summary: Do you use your Permeation Quirk while out photographing for your job, do you just pop out of a wall for a one on one interview...
question: Do you use your Permeation Quirk while out photographing for your job, do you just pop out of a wall for a one on one interview with pro heroes?
answer:
Well, my quirk would have been like a dream-come-true to journalists if that was possible… But unfortunately, it isn’t that easy.

First, I can permeate walls to run around the crime scenes, but my camera and other equipment can’t since it is not part of my body! So it would be very hard for me to calculate every time how to move around with all my equipment: Notepad, camera, pen, recorder, cell phone… sometimes even a laptop.

Secondly, even if I were to permeate through floors or walls, if I come back out… Well… I would be clothless(!!). I’m not a pro-hero myself, so I can’t ask for a special costume to prevent such tragedy too…

Also since I never polished my quirk as well as Mirio, I can only do really basic stuff with my quirk… If I use it without training, my body would be split into two.

In anyhow, my quirk is still useful to dodge attacks from villains!
